Description:
    Generates a new tool that inherits from ApplicationTool

Example:
    rails generate tool NAME

    This will create:
        app/tools/NAME_tool.rb
        spec/tools/NAME_tool_spec.rb

    Example:
        rails generate tool fetch_user

    This will create:
        app/tools/fetch_user_tool.rb
        spec/tools/fetch_user_tool_spec.rb 
